{
  "name": "Lightning Arrow",
  "_id": "matSplLightningA",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>As your attack hits or misses the target, the weapon or ammunition you're using transforms into a lightning bolt. Instead of taking any damage or other effects from the attack, the target takes 4d8 Lightning damage in addition to the weapon's normal damage on a hit or half as much damage on a miss. Each creature within 10 feet of the target then makes a Dexterity saving throw, taking 2d8 Lightning damage on a failed save or half as much damage on a successful one.</p><p>The weapon or ammunition then returns to its normal form.</p><p><strong>Using a Higher-Level Spell Slot.</strong> The damage for both effects of the spell increases by 1d8 for each spell slot level above 3.</p>",
